Ing '''''Nagarakretagama''''' o '''''Nagarakrtagama''''', a ausan da mu namang '''''Desawarnana''''', metung yang patungkul king [[Matwang Amanung Java]] kang [[Hayam Wuruk]], metung a [[ari]]ng tau [[Java]] ampong emperador ning [[Imperyong Majapahit]].  Sinulat neng [[Mpu Prapanca]] anyang [[1365]] (or 1287 [[Panaun a Shalivahana|banwang Saka]]).<ref name="Myron">{{cite journal|title=The Study of The Artistic Antiquities of Dutch India|journal=Harvard Journal of Asiatic Studies|author=Myron Malkiel-Jirmounsky|volume=4|issue=1|month=May|year=1939|pages=59&ndash;68|publisher=Harvard-Yenching Institute|doi=10.2307/2717905|jstor=2717905}}</ref>  Atin yang detalyadung pamilarawan ing ''Nagarakretagama'' ning Imperyung Majapahit anyang pekamaleparan ya iti. Patuwan na ning kawatasan ing ulaga ning [[Hindu]]–[[Buddhismu]] king Imperyung Majapahit kapamilatan ning pamaglarawan kareng templu ampong palasyu, ampo mapilan a seremonyas.

